<h1>Import bands</h1>

<p>Upload a YAML file that is an array of Band hashes.  This will currently look up an existing Band by name and update the associated columns.<p>
<p>For example:<p>
<pre>
---
- :name: Alpha
  :popularity: 3.14
- :name: Beta
  :popularity: 4.20
</pre>

<%= form_tag({:action => :import}, :multipart => true) do %>
  <div class="field">
    <%= file_field_tag :file %><br />
    <%= submit_tag "Upload file" %>
  </div>
<% end %>
